OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772478694
OL,3,CTrams not running across whole of
OL,4,CNottingham
OL,6,FAll Nottingham Express Transit (NET)
OL,7,Ftram services have been cancelled
OL,8,Fbecause of 'network-wide issues'.
OL,10,FDisruption continues after damage to
OL,11,Foverhead lines earlier this week. The
OL,12,Fhope for the network was that some
OL,13,Fservices would still be running
OL,14,Fheading into the weekend. But at
OL,15,F5.50am this morning, NET confirmed it
OL,16,Fhas no running services at all.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
