OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772478694
OL,3,CTrams not running across whole of
OL,4,CNottingham
OL,6,FIn a statement it said: "Following
OL,7,Fyesterday's disruption, we're now
OL,8,Fexperiencing network-wide issues, and
OL,9,Ftherefore, we have no tram services
OL,10,Foperating at any of our stops across
OL,11,Fthe network.
OL,13,F"All Nottingham City Transport
OL,14,Fservices will accept tram tickets and
OL,15,Ftravel cards."
OL,17,F"We're working to fix the issue and
OL,18,Fwill keep you updated as soon as the
OL,19,Fsituation changes".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
