CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772478694
OL,3,CTrams not running across whole of
OL,4,CNottingham
OL,6,F"Customers wishing to park at the
OL,7,FForest Park & Ride and walk into the
OL,8,FCity may do so. Our parking attendants
OL,9,Fhave been stood down until our
OL,10,Fservices resume".
OL,12,FThe exact nature of the issues
OL,13,Faffecting the issue are yet to be
OL,14,Fconfirmed.
